org.ftccommunity.org.ftccommunity.ftcxtensible.services

Class ServiceManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ftccommunity.org.ftccommunity.ftcxtensible.services.ServiceManager

  • public class ServiceManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Manages user-defined Services. It handles any services defined by the RobotService annonation and handles passing the RobotContext to the services who also implement LatebindingContextService, however if a Service only implements LatebindingContextService the Service will not be handled
    Since:
    0.3.2
    Author:
    David Sargent
